---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Automation Software Engineer specializing in IIoT solutions"
	pubDate={new Date('March 3 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<h2>Professional Summary</h2>
	<p><a href="/ibrahimcan_ozdogan_CV.pdf" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:underline;">Download My CV</a></p>
	<div class="cv-preview">
		<iframe src="/ibrahimcan_ozdogan_CV.pdf" width="100%" height="500" title="CV preview"></iframe>
	</div>
	<p>
		I'm an Automation Software & IIoT Engineer with a passion for designing intelligent systems that bridge 
		the physical and digital worlds. With expertise in industrial IoT platforms, real-time software, and 
		embedded systems, I develop scalable solutions that drive operational efficiency and innovation.
	</p>

	<h2>Areas of Expertise</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Industrial IoT (IIoT)</strong> - Edge computing, sensor integration, data acquisition</li>
		<li><strong>Automation Software</strong> - Control systems, real-time processing, protocol implementations</li>
		<li><strong>Embedded Systems</strong> - Microcontroller programming, firmware development</li>
		<li><strong>Full Stack Development</strong> - Web dashboards, mobile apps, backend services</li>
		<li><strong>System Architecture</strong> - Scalable infrastructure, cloud integration, edge-cloud hybrid solutions</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Technical Skills</h2>
	<p>
		<strong>Programming Languages:</strong> C, C++, Python, JavaScript, TypeScript, Java<br/>
		<strong>Platforms & Tools:</strong> Arduino, STM32, Raspberry Pi, Edge Impulse, Node-RED<br/>
		<strong>IoT Protocols:</strong> MQTT, CoAP, OPC UA, Modbus, CAN bus<br/>
		<strong>Cloud & Databases:</strong> AWS IoT Core, Azure, Firebase, PostgreSQL, MongoDB<br/>
		<strong>Development Tools:</strong> Git, Docker, Kubernetes, VS Code, PlatformIO
	</p>

	<h2>Education</h2>
	<p>
		I hold a degree in Software Engineering with focus on embedded systems and industrial automation. 
		Continuously updating my skills through certifications and hands-on projects in emerging IoT technologies.
	</p>

	<h2>What Drives Me</h2>
	<p>
		I believe in the power of connected systems to solve real-world challenges. Whether it's optimizing 
		manufacturing processes, improving predictive maintenance, or enabling smart infrastructure, I'm committed 
		to building solutions that make a tangible impact. I document my journey through technical blogs, 
		open-source contributions, and detailed project case studies.
	</p>

	<h2>Beyond Code</h2>
	<p>
		When I'm not working on automation projects, you'll find me exploring new IoT frameworks, 
		contributing to open-source communities, or sharing knowledge through technical writing and mentoring.
	</p>

